            <thetext>Model items will be applied to layout widgets through the cell renderer in ascending order. But the items from pool will be returned in descending order.

That behavior is not really a problem but syncing of the both orders can increase the performance on resizing the virtual widget.

Therefor I would recommended to change the returning order of pooled widgets to ascending.</thetext>
